seams.what_it_does:
The draft-level driver. Splits the draft into sentences (3649), pre-filters content-empty and web-chrome units out of the denominator (3672-3684), then verifies each survivor (serial or via a bounded ThreadPoolExecutor, 3693-3745) and partitions on the single boolean:

    for v in _findings_results:
        if v.is_verified:
            kept.append(v)
        else:
            dropped.append(v)

Returns a StrictVerificationReport carrying kept_sentences / dropped_sentences.
